":"歡迎學術討論&nbsp;"},{"pid":"9cef5592eba256922c7f4cdaad863e368f489de5","tid":1297790,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f67d0cefe3744d2b577dc908f6817a22afd63125","tid":1297790,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"我冇野講，我要見律師"},{"pid":"0bbb2f8f5886cd904db0d994b62cd1b8ffbb5ad4","tid":1297790,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e136e3355da08c4ff1ab769f77727f7a5844c6f","tid":1297790,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"lm聽朝再詳細睇"},{"pid":"1b8d3eac995acfc35a346605ef93f9692ceea3c7","tid":1297790,"uid":84068,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"根本唔想比你走 局黎 放你去到旺角就收網<br />\n旺角佢地主場黎 佔旺魚蛋玩到熟哂啦"},{"pid":"ba5cab664a699529785ec8a6b28c77bc5fd22255","tid":1297790,"uid":36612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得咁撚多cam man"},{"pid":"000839f73902ec4a55ba6f1a93b1088d6a7cc813","tid":1297790,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"歡迎學術討論&nbsp;"},{"pid":"f993e07eafeeed67a4e66ff2f3d3e7bbaf2efe1c","tid":1297790,"uid":118039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7575966499477900870f2a2b34865f86e5dd6473","tid":1297790,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"有咩用"},{"pid":"fa238d6595f5f0823cc5d7c835cd7c1c10d9b43a","tid":1297790,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220de217c5728d8b72c26b5bd7e8b9ee4e717387","tid":1297790,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b8d3eac995acfc35a346605ef93f9692ceea3c7","tid":1297790,"uid":84068,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"根本唔想比你走 局黎 放你去到旺角就收網<br />\n旺角佢地主場黎 佔旺魚蛋玩到熟哂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"個陶輝根本特登"},{"pid":"bb5274e69f4cb5f14adef97f4fc74574cec5fa1c","tid":1297790,"uid":76395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"bookmark左先"},{"pid":"54573259c8abdcfc4decbaa80b4890bc59084980","tid":1297790,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"099cecc6dc8e71dd6338c3e13123e4ffffe565f0","tid":1297790,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3cf5aa9ede8690b4bb6f6a54a2d0b14e01ead95","tid":1297790,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7575966499477900870f2a2b34865f86e5dd6473","tid":1297790,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"有咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該淨係學術交流有用"},{"pid":"d0c1801ff4c480557ba64b0d1935cd8125d8f87f","tid":1297790,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b65024f4b1c6e08cc668cfe86aa560f1babb1017","tid":1297790,"uid":24615,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"結論：如果有cam影到你扔野&gt;比人制服&gt;比人查身分證<br />\n既全程 就好易入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n否則d片有長空白期 或者冇片，要靠狗既供詞 <br />\n<br />\n狗講既野就好易有bug（有第三方既片證明更佳）<br />\n就告唔入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說有冇告得入既案例睇下"},{"pid":"a11ab45e5e468dd8cf9dcdf95a84038df0925adb","tid":1297790,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3899f14346de4cf20ec1a04b6642db134b143e45","tid":1297790,"uid":269982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:21:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"095b002301f50b080d942402de9910d11b2acfa3","tid":1297790,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a929be38980eecd8406cf114ce2d19b5b7210184","tid":1297790,"uid":24615,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"所以以後全部示威者都全黑 個個一樣樣<br />\n避免被一take過影到犯案&gt;被拉<br />\n就好難告得入<br />\n<br />\n因為警察就算現場拘捕，都好難認人認出/證明你就係扔磚果個<br />\n<br />\n同時比人check到八達通/地址都唔大問題<br />\n除非有連續既cam影到你扔野&gt;走佬&gt;嘟卡"},{"pid":"9997f880d84cfdc62bbedf05ee49e16eddf69d53","tid":1297790,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"推正經po"},{"pid":"7c70648caa87947f11f3f52d949e8a455a8e1cd2","tid":1297790,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb2e145e04b911141d5c63f877df7ba0bd5482","tid":1297790,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"603db9e797e54fd344a1d3da329eb23a2add44b7","tid":1297790,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"唔識野無得討論 只可以幫推"},{"pid":"a0ecba0f682e5c5ab6879cc83bd92e2bb678e53b","tid":1297790,"uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"當然暴動罪呢條on9係麻煩少少 <br />\n因為無記錯定性做暴動 就出現過係現場都有機會奶野<br />\n<br />\n所以一定唔可以現場被捕<br />\n<br />\n走佬一定要行到範圍外既地鐵站上車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n走佬&gt;走出範圍&gt;上車 <br />\n唔可以比人連續影到"},{"pid":"aadbf801b4c50e4fad6005f32f5a528a9d2114e8","tid":1297790,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor